<inglise> Whereas it should be laid down that hops prepared from hops certified unprepared may themselves be certified only if preparation is carried out within a closed operating circuit; whereas, however, if these operations take place in certification centres or warehouses the procedure for subsequent certification should be simplified; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks s&auml;testada, et t&ouml;&ouml;tlemata kujul sertifitseeritud humalast valmistatud humalat v&otilde;ib sertifitseerida &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui t&ouml;&ouml;tlemine toimub suletud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisringis; kui k&otilde;nealused toimingud leiavad aset sertifitseerimiskeskustes v&otilde;i -ladudes, tuleks j&auml;rgmiste sertifitseerimiste menetlust lihtsustada; </eesti>
