<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Regulation: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses kasutatakse j&auml;rgmisi m&otilde;isteid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) "unprepared hops" means hops which have undergone only preliminary drying and packaging; </inglise>
<eesti> a) t&ouml;&ouml;tlemata humal - humal, mida on kuivatatud ja pakitud vaid korra; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) "prepared hops" means hops which have undergone final drying and final packaging; </inglise>
<eesti> b) t&ouml;&ouml;deldud humal - humal, mis on l&otilde;plikult kuivatatud ja pakitud; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) "seeded hops" means hops marketed with a seed content greater than 2 % of their weight; </inglise>
<eesti> c) seemnetega humal - humal, mille seemnesisaldus on suurem kui 2% massist; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) "seedless hops" means hops marketed with a seed content not exceeding 2 % of their weight; </inglise>
<eesti> c) seemneteta humal - humal, mille seemnesisaldus ei &uuml;leta 2% massist; </eesti>
<inglise> (e) "isomerized extract of hops" means an extract in which the alpha acids have been almost totally isomerized; </inglise>
<eesti> e) isomeeritud humalaekstrakt - ekstrakt, milles alfahapped on peaaegu t&auml;ielikult isomeeritud; </eesti>
<inglise> (f) "sealing" means closure of the package under official supervision and in such a way that the means of closure will be damaged when the package is opened; </inglise>
<eesti> f) pitseerimine - pakendi sulgemine ametliku j&auml;relevalve all nii, et pakendi avamisel sulgemisvahendid rikutakse; </eesti>
<inglise> (g) "closed operating circuit" means a process for preparing or processing hops carried out under official supervision and in such a way that only one entry is available for the original materials and one exit for prepared or processed products and that no hops or processed products can be added or removed during the operation; </inglise>
<eesti> g) suletud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisring - humala valmistamis- v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisprotsess, mis viiakse l&auml;bi ametliku j&auml;relevalve all nii, et algup&auml;rased tooted sisenevad ja valmis- v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;deldud tooted v&auml;ljuvad ainult &uuml;he korra, ilma v&otilde;imaluseta lisada v&otilde;i k&otilde;rvaldada humalaid v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;deldud tooteid k&otilde;nealuse toimingu jooksul; </eesti>
<inglise> (h) "consignment" means a number of packages of hops or derived products with the same characteristics presented at the same time for certification by the same individual or associated producer or by the same processor. </inglise>
<eesti> h) partii - hulk pakendeid, mis sisaldavad humalat v&otilde;i humalast saadud samade omadustega tooteid, ja mille on esitanud sertifitseerimiseks samal ajal sama &uuml;ksiktootja v&otilde;i tootjate &uuml;hendusse kuuluv tootja v&otilde;i sama t&ouml;&ouml;tleja. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Every consignment of hop cones presented for certification shall be accompanied by a written declaration signed by the producer giving: </inglise>
