<inglise> Article 9 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> While they are in circulation, hop powders and hop extracts may not undergo a change of packaging within the meaning of Article 1 (5) of Regulation (EEC) No 1784/77, unless this is done under official supervision. </inglise>
