<inglise> Article 10 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 10 </eesti>
<inglise> The products referred to in Article 1 (1) (a) to (d) of Regulation (EEC) No 1784/77 shall be subject to the following checks: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1784/77 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 punktides a-d nimetatud tooteid kontrollitakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) In the case of hops harvested on land owned by a brewer and used by him in the natural or processed state: </inglise>
